segmentosSRT.text:
- Shouldn't we run, too?
- Where to?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_16

segmentosSRT.text: I'll hit him again if I have to.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_16

segmentosSRT.text: Sit then. Right in front of me!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_16

segmentosSRT.text: You little bastard! I'll break your legs!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_16

segmentosSRT.text: Red Guards are swarming over the place.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_16

segmentosSRT.text:
I just caught them on a ladder,
pulling off roof tiles.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_16

segmentosSRT.text: No idea! The leader is a cripple.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_16

segmentosSRT.text: We've been through the valley of death.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_16

segmentosSRT.text: Did he eat all seven buns?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_16
